summary:
This model was updated in early 2013, after CR designated it a Don't Buy Safety Risk because an <em>unharnessed</em> child could &quot;submarine&quot; beneath the grab bar. &nbsp;His legs and torso could pass beneath it, but his head could get stuck. &nbsp;The child could be killed or seriously injured. &nbsp; Mutsy has redesigned the grab bar and eliminated the submarining problem. &nbsp;Look for samples with a manufacture date of 01-2013 (JANUARY 2013) or later,&nbsp;when buying. &nbsp;&nbsp;<br />
<br />
We re-tested the stroller with the new grab bar design, and it is very good. &nbsp;
